{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-the-box-model/the-box-model-lesson-g","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Dodajte ivicu svakom elementu na stranici i pogledajte kako su kutije raspoređene.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-the-box-model","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/odin-project/the-box-model/box-model-lines.png\" alt=\"an image showing the odin project website surrounded by red borders indicating that the site is build out of multiple components\" style=\"width: 95%; height: 95%;\">\n<p>U redu, možda na slici iznad postoje krugovi... ali kada je u pitanju raspored, oni se ponašaju kao pravougaone kutije, a ne kao krugovi. Na kraju krajeva, raspoređivanje veb stranice i svih njenih delova svodi se na odlučivanje kako ćete organizovati i rasporediti te kutije.</p>\n<p>Jedini pravi izazov ovde je što postoji mnogo načina za kontrolu veličine ovih kutija i razmaka između njih pomoću unutrašnjeg odstojanja, margine i ivice. Ukratko:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>padding</code> huongeza nafasi kati ya mpaka wa boksi na maudhui ya boksi.</li>\n<li><code>margin</code> dodaje prostor između ivica kutije i ivica susednih kutija.</li>\n<li><code>border</code> dodaje prostor (čak i ako je širok samo jedan ili dva piksela) između margine i unutrašnjeg odstojanja.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hakikisha unakagua michoro kwa makini.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/odin-project/the-box-model/the-box-model.png\" alt=\"Visual representation of CSS box model with text, surrounded by 'padding' in pink, a purple 'border', and 'margin' indicated by blue arrows, explaining space between text, box edge, and window edge.\">\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-the-box-model/the-box-model-lesson-g"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Od unutra ka spolja, kojim redosledom idu svojstva modela kutije?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Content, Margin, Padding, Border</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Margin, Padding, Content, Border</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Sadržaj, Padding, Border, Margin</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Padding, Content, Border, Margin</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Učenje modela kutije G","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-the-box-model","dashedName":"the-box-model-lesson-g","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-the-box-model","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-the-box-model/the-box-model-lesson-h","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-the-box-model/the-box-model-lesson-f","id":"64a6702e7a7d00f97013ed0e","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":15,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-the-box-model/the-box-model-lesson-g"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}